'''James K. Beattie''' is an Australian chemist from [[University of Sydney]] and an Elected Fellow of the [[American Association for the Advancement of Science]] and [[Royal Society of Chemistry]].<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.aaas.org/fellow/beattie-james |title=James Beattie |publisher=aaas.org |accessdate=May 13, 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sydney.edu.au/science/chemistry/news-events/articles/issue-25/testimonials-for-james-beattie.shtml |title=James Beattie |publisher=sydney.edu.au |accessdate=May 13, 2017}}</ref>

